definition: a person who weeps

name: ignoramus
definition: an ignorant person

name: incompetent
definition: someone who is not competent to take effective action

name: novice
definition: someone new to a field or activity

name: intruder
definition: someone who intrudes on the privacy or property of another without permission

name: meddler
definition: an officious annoying person who interferes with others

name: troublemaker
definition: someone who deliberately stirs up trouble

name: unpleasant person
definition: a person who is not pleasant or agreeable

name: villain
definition: a wicked or evil person; someone who does evil deliberately

name: consumer
definition: a person who uses goods or services

name: idealist
definition: someone guided more by ideals than by practical considerations

name: guerrilla
definition: a member of an irregular armed force that fights a stronger force by sabotage and harassment

name: white man
definition: a man who is White

name: semite
definition: a member of a group of Semitic-speaking peoples of the Middle East and northern Africa

name: assistant
definition: a person who contributes to the fulfillment of a need or furtherance of an effort or purpose

name: boatman
definition: someone who drives or rides in a boat

name: collector (worker)
definition: a person who is employed to collect payments (as for rent or taxes)

name: driver (worker)
definition: someone who drives animals that pull a vehicle

name: employee
definition: a worker who is hired to perform a job

name: quarryman
definition: a man who works in a quarry

name: servant
definition: a person working in the service of another (especially in the household)

name: skilled worker
definition: a worker who has acquired special skills

name: volunteer (worker)
definition: a person who performs voluntary work

name: washer (worker)
definition: someone who washes things for a living

name: gloxinia
definition: any of several plants of the genera Gloxinia or Sinningia (greenhouse gloxinias) having showy bell-shaped flowers

name: aconite
definition: any of various usually poisonous plants of the genus Aconitum having tuberous roots and palmately lobed leaves and blue or white flowers

name: baneberry (poisonous plant)
definition: a plant of the genus Actaea having acrid poisonous berries

name: dogbane
definition: any of several poisonous perennial plants of the genus Apocynum having acrid milky juice and bell-shaped white or pink flowers and a very bitter root

name: hellebore (poisonous plant)
definition: any plant of the Eurasian genus Helleborus

name: aquatic plant
definition: a plant that grows partly or wholly in water whether rooted in the mud, as a lotus, or floating without anchorage, as the water hyacinth

name: bulbous plant
definition: plant growing from a bulb

name: cormous plant
definition: plant growing from a corm

name: desert plant
definition: plant adapted for life with a limited supply of water; compare hydrophyte and mesophyte

name: herb
definition: a plant lacking a permanent woody stem; many are flowering garden plants or potherbs; some having medicinal properties; some are pests

name: pteridophyte
definition: plants having vascular tissue and reproducing by spores

name: spermatophyte
definition: plant that reproduces by means of seeds not spores

name: succulent
definition: a plant adapted to arid conditions and characterized by fleshy water-storing tissues that act as water reservoirs

name: vine
definition: a plant with a weak stem that derives support from climbing, twining, or creeping along a surface

name: weed (vascular plant)
definition: any plant that crowds out cultivated plants

name: woody plant
definition: a plant having hard lignified tissues or woody parts especially stems

name: wildflower
definition: wild or uncultivated flowering plant

name: meson
definition: an elementary particle responsible for the forces in the atomic nucleus; a hadron with a baryon number of 0

name: nucleon
definition: a constituent (proton or neutron) of an atomic nucleus

name: electron
definition: an elementary particle with negative charge

name: down (feather)
definition: soft fine feathers

name: flight feather
definition: any of the larger wing or tail feathers of a bird

name: coat (hair)
definition: growth of hair or wool or fur covering the body of an animal

name: facial hair
definition: hair on the face (especially on the face of a man)

name: hairdo
definition: the arrangement of the hair (especially a woman's hair)

name: lock (hair)
definition: a strand or cluster of hair

name: scute
definition: large bony or horny plate as on an armadillo or turtle or the underside of a snake

name: bract
definition: a modified leaf or leaflike part just below and protecting an inflorescence

name: hull (husk)
definition: dry outer covering of a fruit or seed or nut

name: ascocarp
definition: mature fruiting body of an ascomycetous fungus

name: compound leaf
definition: a leaf composed of a number of leaflets on a common stalk

name: floral leaf
definition: a modified leaf that is part of a flower

name: simple leaf
definition: a leaf that is not divided into parts

name: sporophyll
definition: leaf in ferns and mosses that bears the sporangia

name: agamete
definition: an asexual reproductive cell

name: cone (reproductive structure)
definition: cone-shaped mass of ovule- or spore-bearing scales or bracts

name: flower (reproductive structure)
definition: reproductive organ of angiosperm plants especially one having showy or colorful parts

name: fruit
definition: the ripened reproductive body of a seed plant

name: gametoecium
definition: gametangia and surrounding bracts

name: ovule (reproductive structure)
definition: a small body that contains the female germ cell of a plant; develops into a seed after fertilization

name: pistil
definition: the female ovule-bearing part of a flower composed of ovary and style and stigma

name: placentation
definition: arrangement of the ovules in the placenta and of the placentas in the ovary

name: sporangium
definition: organ containing or producing spores

name: style
definition: (botany) the narrow elongated part of the pistil between the ovary and the stigma

name: bud (sprout)
definition: a swelling on a plant stem consisting of overlapping immature leaves or petals

name: shoot
definition: a new branch

name: axis (stalk)
definition: the main stem or central part about which plant organs or plant parts such as branches are arranged

name: branch
definition: a division of a stem, or secondary stem arising from the main stem of a plant

name: bulb (stalk)
definition: a modified bud consisting of a thickened globular underground stem serving as a reproductive structure

name: cane (stalk)
definition: a strong slender often flexible stem as of bamboos, reeds, rattans, or sugar cane

name: scape
definition: erect leafless flower stalk growing directly from the ground as in a tulip

name: tuber
definition: a fleshy underground stem or root serving for reproductive and food storage

name: neuroglia
definition: sustentacular tissue that surrounds and supports neurons in the central nervous system; glial and neural cells together compose the tissue of the central nervous system

name: vascular bundle
definition: a unit strand of the vascular system in stems and leaves of higher plants consisting essentially of xylem and phloem

name: smear
definition: a thin tissue or blood sample spread on a glass slide and stained for cytologic examination and diagnosis under a microscope
